==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: mugger
<hw>mugger</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A thief who takes property by
threatening (or performing) violence on the person who is robbed; a
person who commits a mugging; one who mugs. See <er>mug</er>, <pos>v.
t.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> robber</syn>⟦br⟧
